    <h3>Multi-Agent Orchestration & Workflow Engine</h3>
    <p>
        The platform leverages <strong>OpenAI function calling</strong> to create intelligent agents that can 
        autonomously select and execute tools based on context. Each agent has a specialized role (research, reporting, 
        email, operations) and can collaborate with other agents in sequential workflows. The workflow engine executes 
        agents step-by-step, passing output from one agent to the next, with comprehensive logging of each step, tool 
        call, and result. Users can create complex multi-step automations through the visual workflow builder, defining 
        agent sequences and monitoring execution in real-time.
    </p>
