    <h3>Workflow Builder & Execution</h3>
    <p>
        The <strong>visual workflow builder</strong> allows users to create complex multi-agent workflows with an intuitive 
        interface. Workflows are defined as sequences of agents, where each agent receives input from the previous step and 
        passes its output to the next. The system supports asynchronous execution for long-running workflows, with detailed 
        logging of each step, tool invocation, and result. The run viewer provides step-by-step visualization of executions, 
        showing tool calls, parameters, results, and execution times for complete transparency and debugging.
    </p>
