    <h3>Integrated Tools & Extensibility</h3>
    <p>
        The platform features a <strong>modular tool layer</strong> designed for extensibility. Integrated tools include 
        Web Search (via Tavily API), Email (SMTP or API providers like Resend), Google Calendar (with OAuth for reading 
        and creating events), and Database Operations (secure typed APIs, no raw SQL). Each tool is exposed to agents 
        through OpenAI function calling, allowing the LLM to intelligently select and execute tools based on context. 
        The tool layer is designed to be easily extensible, allowing new tools to be added without modifying core orchestration logic.
    </p>
